<strong><br />
Amy, this is so nice to hear, and I bet you have plenty of great ideas yourself. If you&#8217;re ever interested in sending in a <a href="//learning.blogs.nytimes.com/category/great-ideas-from-readers/" rel="nofollow">Reader Idea</a>, we&#8217;d love to know how you&#8217;re using The Times with your students. Thanks for taking the time to write in. &#8211;Katherine</strong></p>

